Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(316,460)}－Yack Deculture!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到，真的會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Antares1，確認效果\N開始進行清剿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各機，不要落後了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能活下來的只能是你們\N或是我們其中之一的話，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感情係數被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還遠遠需要調教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢復反應了
