Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭卡，蘭卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開，Skull4！
